OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FAn emergency plan has been triggered
OL,7,Fby the government to ease overcrowding
OL,8,Fin which could mean some court
OL,9,Fhearings are delayed.
OL,11,FThe mechanism, called Operation Early
OL,12,FDawn, is expected to be in action for
OL,13,Fa week.
OL,15,FThe measure is a long-standing
OL,16,Fcontingency plan, and allows
OL,17,Fdefendants to be held in police cells
OL,18,Funtil prison beds become available,
OL,19,Fbut could mean their court dates are
OL,20,Fdelayed or adjourned.
