OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FIt allows the prison service to make
OL,7,Fjudgements each morning on whether
OL,8,Fprisoners are taken to courts or
OL,9,Fremain in police cells.
OL,11,FJustice officials are yet to confirm
OL,12,Fhow many cases will be affected but
OL,13,Fstressed the measures, while rolled
OL,14,Fout across England, do not mean there
OL,15,Fwill be delays in every region and
OL,16,Finsisted the plan was put in place to
OL,17,Flimit disruption.
