OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FITV News understands the current
OL,7,Flocations where the plan is being
OL,8,Factivated are London and the North
OL,9,FEast.
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Justice said: "We
OL,12,Fcontinue to see pressure on our
OL,13,Fprisons following the impact of the
OL,14,Fpandemic and barristers' strike which
OL,15,Fis why we have initiated a previously
OL,16,Fused measure to securely transfer
OL,17,Fprisoners between courts and custody
OL,18,Fand ensure there is always a custody
OL,19,Fcell available should they be
OL,20,Fremanded."
