OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FIt comes as Sir Keir Starmer urged
OL,7,FRishi Sunak to stop trying to issue
OL,8,F"get out of jail free cards" to
OL,9,Fcriminals during Prime Minister's
OL,10,FQuestions, comparing the Prime
OL,11,FMinister to a "jumped-up milk monitor".
OL,13,FThe Labour leader referenced another
OL,14,Fgovernment scheme which allows some
OL,15,Flow-level offenders to be released
OL,16,Fearly, and is due to be extended from
OL,17,Fnext week to allow sentences to be cut
OL,18,Fby up to 70 days.
