OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FSir Keir accused the Tory government
OL,7,Fof causing "chaos" in the prison
OL,8,Fsystem, asking "does the prime
OL,9,Fminister think that his decision to
OL,10,Fallow prisoners out 70 days early
OL,11,Fmakes our country more secure?"
OL,13,FThe government's End of Custody
OL,14,FSupervised License Scheme (ECSL)
OL,15,Finitially involved inmates being
OL,16,Freleased up to 18 days early. That was
OL,17,Fthen , and will be further extended to
OL,18,F70 days from 23 May.
