OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FA row broke out during PMQs over
OL,7,Fwhether prisoners who are considered
OL,8,Fhigh risk will be released under the
OL,9,Fscheme, after a report from the
OL,10,Fprison's inspector said high risk
OL,11,Foffenders including a domestic abuser
OL,12,Fwho posed a risk to children had been
OL,13,Freleased.
OL,15,FCharlie Taylor's report said he had
OL,16,F"serious concerns" about the early
OL,17,Frelease scheme, citing an inmate at
OL,18,FHMP Lewes who posed a danger to
OL,19,Fchildren having his release date
OL,20,Fbrought forward.
