OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FIn light of this report, Sir Keir
OL,7,Fpressed the PM for assurance on
OL,8,Fwhether the prisoners being let out
OL,9,Fearly are "considered to be high risk."
OL,11,FMr Sunak responded by saying: "Let me
OL,12,Fbe crystal clear, no-one would be put
OL,13,Fon the scheme if they were deemed a
OL,14,Fthreat to the public. Offenders are
OL,15,Fsubject to the toughest of licensing
OL,16,Fconditions, and if those conditions
OL,17,Fare broken, they are back in prison
OL,18,Ffor considerably longer."
