OL,6,FBut there are significant concerns
OL,7,Fthat people convicted of domestic
OL,8,Fviolence are being released under the
OL,9,Fscheme.
OL,11,FAbigail Ampofo CEO of the domestic
OL,12,Fviolence charity Refuge said this
OL,13,Fannouncement was a "disappointing
OL,14,Fsuprise" and will have a "huge impact"
OL,15,Fon survivors of domestic abuse.
