OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,F"One of the things we know is domestic
OL,7,Fabuse is poorly understood, it's not
OL,8,Fneccessarily the easiest crime to be
OL,9,Fable to achieve a prosecution for, and
OL,10,Fnot knowing when your perpetrator is
OL,11,Fgoing to be released not only puts you
OL,12,Fat physical risk, but there's a huge
OL,13,Famount of psychological concern and
OL,14,Flack of safety."
OL,16,FThe Labour leader criticised the PM
OL,17,Ffor focusing too much on, rather than
OL,18,Fon issues like the "prison system in
OL,19,Fchaos".
