OL,6,FThe government blame overcrowding in
OL,7,FUK jails on pressures during the
OL,8,Fpandemic and industrial action by
OL,9,Fbarristers in 2022. But prisons
OL,10,Fwatchdog Charlie Taylor has branded
OL,11,Fthe situation "entirely predictable".
