OL,3,CEmergency plan triggered by government
OL,4,Cin a bid to ease overcrowding in jails
OL,6,FDavid McNeill, Director of Public
OL,7,FAffairs and the Law Society told ITV
OL,8,FNews this scheme could increase the
OL,9,Frisk to the public: "some defendants
OL,10,Fwho would otherwise normally be held
OL,11,Fin prison on remand, because of the
OL,12,Fseverity of the case or the risk of
OL,13,Frunning away, will now instead be
OL,14,Fgiven bail and will be free."
OL,16,F"The whole of the criminal justice
OL,17,Fsystrem is in crisis, there's been a
OL,18,Flack of investment for over a decade",
OL,19,Fhe said.
